div.div:
This class need to read a line in input and create a PureCommand
- the goal is to try to Tokenize and crete a command even if the line
is not well written
- the class does not know about all different sensors and parameters
These are the commands supported:
- get {SENSOR};
- SENSOR
- temperature
- humidity
- set-notify {SENSOR} ({PARAMA} {VAL}, {PARAMA} {VAL},);
- SENSOR:
- PARAM VAL
- temperature
- min val
- max val
- diff val
- time val
